      <para>Open the cell format dialog. This dialog can be opened from the
         <guimenu>Format</guimenu><guimenuitem>Cells</guimenuitem> menu,
         with the <keycombo><keycap>Ctrl</keycap><keycap>1</keycap></keycombo>,
